Start time : 24/04/2023 15:00 UTC End time : 24/07/2023 15:00 UTC Service impact : None Service improvement : As part of our product lifecycle management, we have decided to end the access of its predecessor: Urchin statistics collection service. It won't be available from Monday 24 april 2023. Since 2021, we have made available our new tool to display your website statistics, called OVHcloud Web Statistics which can be accessed with your hosting logs. Documentation about OVHcloud Web Statistics: https://docs.ovh.com/us/en/hosting/shared_view_my_websites_logs_and_statistics/ . Please note that this maintenance only covers Webhosting statistics before February 2020. Statistics after February 2020 are available in Owstats. Logs collection and Daily statistics aren't in the scope of the maintenance. Timeline : Monday 24 April 2023: Closing of the service accessibility Monday 24 April 2023: End of Support, Shutdown of the service Monday 24 July 2023: Data deletion We will update this task during the proposed timeline.

Start time : 24/04/2023 18:00 UTC End time : 24/04/2023 19:00 UTC Service impact : All projects and environments will continue to function during the upgrade; however, Console User Interface, Git and Crons will be unavailable during the reindexing of git logs, which may take up to 6 hours. Service improvement : Our partner communicated to OVHCloud that they will be doing a routine maintenance on customers' projects. This maintenance is expected to not have impact on the projects: no downtime, nor performance issue are expected.
